quran[5{c,v,t}:
60,1,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, agar tum meri raah mein jehaad karne ke liye aur meri Raza joi ki khatir ( watan chore kar gharon se ) niklay ho to mere aur apne dushmanon ko dost nah banaao tum unn ke sath dosti ki terhan daaltay ho, halaank jo haq tumahray paas aaya hai uss ko maan-ne se woh inkaar kar chuke hain aur unn ki rawish yeh hai ke rasool ko aur khud tum ko sirf iss qasoor par jala watan karte hain ke tum apne rab, Allah par imaan laaye ho tum chhupa kar unn ko dostana pegham bhaijtay ho, halaank jo kuch tum chhupa kar karte ho aur jo alania karte ho, har cheez ko mein khoob jaanta hon jo shakhs bhi tum mein se aisa kere woh yaqeenan raah raast se bhatak gaya"
60,2,unn ka rawayya to yeh hai ke agar tum par qaboo pa jayen to tumahray sath dushmani karen aur haath aur zabaan se tumhe azaar den woh to yeh chahtay hain ke tum kisi terhan kafir ho jao
60,3,"qayamat ke din nah tumhari rishta dariyan kisi kaam ayen gi nah tumhari aulaad uss roz Allah tumahray darmain judai daal day ga, aur o hi tumahray aamaal ka dekhnay wala hai"
60,4,"tum logon ke liye ibrahim aur uss ke sathiyon mein aik acha namona hai ke onhon ne apni qoum se saaf keh diya"" hum tum se aur tumahray inn mabodon se jin ko tum khuda ko chore kar pujte ho qatee bezaar hain, hum ne tum se kufar kya aur hamaray aur tumahray darmain hamesha ke liye adawat ho gayi aur bair par gaya jab taq tum Allah wahid par imaan nah lao"" magar ibrahim ka apne baap se yeh kehna ( iss se mustasna hai ) ke"" mein aap ke liye mughfirat ki darkhwast zaroor karoon ga, aur Allah se aap ke liye kuch haasil kar lena mere bas mein nahi hai"" ( aur ibrahim o ashaab ibrahim ki dua yeh thi ke )"" ae hamaray rab, tairay hi oopar hum ne bhrosa kya aur teri hi taraf hum ne rujoo kar liya aur tairay hi huzoor hamein palatna hai"
60,5,"ae hamaray rab, hamein kafiroon ke liye fitnah nah bana day aur ae hamaray rab, hamarayKasoroo-n se dar guzar farma, be shak to hi zabardast aur Dana hai """
